### jira.conf Format

# Jira Configuration
# Used by SM agent to identify project scope

JIRA\_PROJECT\_PREFIX=KSA

### Input Parsing Logic

Input: "KSA workflow"
 → Matches [A-Z]+ (no number) + action
 → Project-level workflow

Input: "KSA-13 tạo BRD"
 → Matches [A-Z]+-\d+ + action
 → Ticket-level workflow

### Glossary

|  |  |
| --- | --- |
| Term | Definition |
| SM Agent | Scrum Master agent — orchestrates the SDLC pipeline |
| jira.conf | Configuration file storing active project prefix |
| Project-level input | SM invocation with project key only (no ticket number) |
| Ticket-level input | SM invocation with specific ticket key (project + number) |
| VSIX | Visual Studio Code Extension package format |

